                    "analysis": "и®?$A$ дёәеҸ‘жҠҘеҸ°еҸ‘еҮәдҝЎеҸ· вҖ?вҖқпјҢ$B$ дёәж”¶жҠҘеҸ°ж”¶еҲ°дҝЎеҸ· вҖ?вҖқпјҢдҫқйўҳж„ҸпјҢ\n$$\n\\begin{aligned}\nP(A) & =0.6, P(\\bar{A})=0.4 \\\\\nP(B \\mid A) & =0.8, P(\\bar{B} \\mid A)=0.2, P(B \\mid \\bar{A})=0.1, P(\\bar{B} \\mid \\bar{A})=0.9\n\\end{aligned}\n$$\nз”ұиҙқеҸ¶ж–Ҝе…¬ејҸ\n$$\n\\begin{aligned}\nP(A \\mid B) & =\\frac{P(A) P(B \\mid A)}{P(A) P(B \\mid A)+P(\\bar{A}) P(B \\mid \\bar{A})}=\\frac{0.6 \\times 0.8}{0.6 \\times 0.8+0.4 \\times 0.1} \\approx 0.923 \\\\\nP(\\bar{A} \\mid \\bar{B}) & =\\frac{P(\\bar{A}) P(\\bar{B} \\mid \\bar{A})}{P(\\bar{A}) P(\\bar{B} \\mid \\bar{A})+P(A) P(\\bar{B} \\mid A)}=\\frac{0.4 \\times 0.9}{0.4 \\times 0.9+0.6 \\times 0.2}=0.75\n\\end{aligned}\n$$",
